A stable and controlled environment was prepared to ensure accurate and repeatable results. The following tools and components were Apache JMeter 5.6.3 . This is used to simulate user load and measure server performance. JMeter's has GUI and  non GUI mode , non GUI are more efficiency because its reduces overhead and provides more accurate results. Furthermore its easier to find the kb and the operation guide for beginner like me to start studies about pentest.

You can download it here : https://jmeter.apache.org/download_jmeter.cgi
Require the java 8+ to working.
Go to the C:\<Location where you extract>\ apache-jmeter-5.6.3\apache-jmeter-5.6.3\bin
Open the jmeter.bat to open the application
